comments: The song should have been launched simultaneously with the TV show / song contest "Canzonissima '68", hosted by Mina. The participants (all famous Italian singers) protested because Mina was given the "Primus inter pares" role, which caused the single to be put temporarily on hold. When it was finally issued, Vartan had already released her own version of the song.
